{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"update","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Use this method to update the appearance of the user location annotation. This","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"method is called by the associated map view when it has determined that the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"user location annotation needs to be updated. This can happen in response to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"user interaction, a change in the user’s location, when the user tracking mode","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"changes, or when the viewport changes.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"During user interaction with the map, this method may be called many","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"times to update the user location annotation. Therefore, your implementation of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"this method should be as lightweight as possible to avoid negatively affecting","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"performance.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"Note","style":"note"}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnuserlocationannotationview\/update"]}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"update"}],"title":"update","symbolKind":"method","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"update","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNUserLocationAnnotatio